---
title: Sichuan-Glazed Beef Rissoles with Sesame Fries & Asian Slaw
description: How to improve beef rissoles? Toss them in our mild Sichuan garlic paste, of course! It adds loads of flavour and that saucy touch that makes every mouthful a delight. Fries with crisp sesame seeds and slaw coated in Japanese dressing seal the deal.

